snippet.title: October 4, 2011 - Redneck Stuntman
snippet.description: A chubby kid attempts BMX, the Redneck Stuntman gets a Web Redemption, and Daniel makes insane proclamations on Twitter.

snippet.title: October 22, 2013 - Redemption Reunion Spectacular
snippet.description: A devout passenger has a divine fit on an airplane, a woman botches jumping in front of a train, and Daniel revisits Web Redemptions gone by.
